BT /F1 12 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 634.00 Tm (item values. This slows daily work and makes it harder to identify delayed or urgent orders) Tj ET
BT /F1 12 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 618.00 Tm (quickly.) Tj ET
BT /F1 12 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 598.00 Tm (The business need is to create consolidated reports where buyers and procurement) Tj ET
