BT /F1 12 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 492.00 Tm (useful filters, calculated delivery status, drilldown support, vendor performance metrics,) Tj ET
BT /F1 12 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 476.00 Tm (and delivery tracking.) Tj ET
BT /F2 14 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 456.00 Tm (Project Summary) Tj ET
BT /F1 12 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 434.00 Tm (This capstone project focuses on practical MM reporting scenarios. It includes a main PO) Tj ET
BT /F1 12 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 418.00 Tm (analytics report, a vendor performance scorecard, and a delivery tracking tool. The codebase) Tj ET
BT /F1 12 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 402.00 Tm (demonstrates common ABAP skills such as selection-screen design, Open SQL joins, internal-) Tj ET
BT /F1 12 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 386.00 Tm (table processing, ALV display handling, local class-based event handling, and business-rule) Tj ET
BT /F1 12 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 370.00 Tm (implementation while keeping the scope manageable.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 505.00 22.00 Tm (Page 1) Tj ET
