BT /F1 12 Tf 1 0 0 1 50.00 516.00 Tm (- Modular code design with separate include programs following ABAP conventions.) Tj ET
BT /F1 12 Tf 1 0 0 1 50.00 498.00 Tm (- Uses standard SAP MM tables so results can be validated easily in a training system.) Tj ET
BT /F1 12 Tf 1 0 0 1 50.00 480.00 Tm (- Combines reporting, aggregation, event handling, and business status calculation.) Tj ET
BT /F2 14 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 462.00 Tm (Why This Topic Fits an ABAP Developer) Tj ET
