BT /F1 12 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 392.00 Tm (work across related tools within the same functional domain while avoiding unnecessary) Tj ET
BT /F1 12 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 376.00 Tm (complexity.) Tj ET
